 beverages, personal care, and household products; clean energy, is a power generated from renewable, environmentally friendly sources like solar, wind, hydro, and geothermal; and solid and waste water management involves the treatment and disposal of sewage, industrial effluents, and solid waste to protect public health and the environment. The company also offers mobiles, includes mobile marketing solutions, mobile campaigns, mobile wap site, messaging solutions, and m-commerce solutions. In addition, the company offers barrel, includes Drum Manufacturing; waste energy services, such as incineration, gasification, anaerobic digestion, and pyrolysis to recover energy from solid, organic, and industrial waste; and trading of commodities, such as iron and steel, tubes and bars, cast iron products, steel pipes and fittings, and casting & forging materials. It serves retail, brand marketing, manufacturing, communication, education and training, and digital media markets. The company was formerly known as Sylph Technologies limited and changed its name to Sylph Industries Limited in October 2025. The company was incorporated in 1992 and is based in Indore, India."}}